{"tid":1677944,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[爵士]連加特時裝品牌勁蝕20萬鎊","createTime":"2019-10-27T11:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T16:15:26.000Z","uid":31626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"24180b2179b54d515e1d1cf68f114b369d020418","tid":1677944,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/1/151/27323298151/27321215829_561x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F1%2F151%2F27323298151%2F27321215829_561x420.jpg&h=b4aaa1b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports-體育】曼聯攻中連加特在場上表現不濟，場外也不如意，自家時裝品牌首年錄得20萬鎊虧損。<br />\n<br />\n連加特（Jesse Lingard）在去年12月推出時裝品牌JLINGZ，希望仿效球王基斯坦奴朗拿度，借自己於曼聯及英格蘭代表隊累積的人氣，在場外發大財。<br />\n<br />\n雖然連加特已不時在個人Instagram狂sell JLINGZ的產品，但銷情仍然慘淡。根據英國《太陽報》指，JLINGZ於今年1月31日前，已經虧損了211688鎊。<br />\n<br />\nJLINGZ在去年隆重登場的大型記者會，正正是去年曼聯以1:3不敵利物浦的雙紅會之前，因此連加特招來不少曼聯名宿批評。<br />\n<br />\n堅尼表示：「隊友不應該忍受這樣的行為。」加利尼維利則認為：「我不反對他經營時裝品牌，但不應該在作客利物浦這場全季最重要的比賽前夕推出。」"},{"pid":"f8e7883d7727a58df281fbdedfd3b1a0fc3e6522","tid":1677944,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"34b301c0b213f9bcfa83454b22d851652c3f5fe7","tid":1677944,"uid":14983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"兩星期人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4f0f7619e33b02f22cbb2e694770c50a334681","tid":1677944,"uid":111006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"弱智仔先會買佢d產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28818d64cf20176806c39697d566398de54927a8","tid":1677944,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img